{"ts":"2026-05-30T06:08:36.451Z","author":"maintainer-agent","op":"comment_add","patch":[{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/comments/2","value":{"created_at":"2026-05-30T06:08:36.451Z","author":"maintainer-agent","text":"Dogfood evidence: isolated package-first dogfood passed with PM_DOGFOOD_SEMANTIC=1 and qwen3-embedding:0.6b. It exercised 86 commands across init --with-packages, package install/catalog/doctor/upgrade, SDK/runtime contracts, calendar, search/reindex, Plan lifecycle, linked files/docs/tests, health/validate, and release. Slowest expected linked-test run was 3094ms; semantic hybrid reindex was 1038ms; slowest non-test/non-semantic surfaces were plan show deep 525ms, package install all 476ms, package local install 474ms, claim 424ms, plan approve 404ms, package list 380ms."}},{"op":"replace","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-05-30T06:08:36.451Z"}],"before_hash":"2374eaf9f649eb9f6ea597fde3fa79bd824585dea80dcaedf6901e77db5c51ac","after_hash":"81f681f4af8d66d8d8fa07c90cfcc1047f3d427024fb4022042134200c7ba241"}
